						<summary>

						<p>On a slab lying in the ruined Śiva temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara Bētarāja.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka [1500], Virōdhin • • • • .</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Gives a long string of <hi rend="italic">birudas</hi> of the chief. Seems to record the gift of land [to a temple] at Bōḍanipalli.</p>						

						</summary>
